&#123;"requirements":"*<span class&#61;"scp" data-skill&#61;"Quest points" data-level&#61;"16" style&#61;"position:relative;display:inline-block;height:1em;">&#91;&#91;File:Quest point icon.png|link&#61;Quest points|alt&#61;Quest points&#93;&#93; 16 &#91;&#91;Quest points&#93;&#93;</span> <sup>(<span title&#61;"This quest cannot be started without this requirement" style&#61;"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;">required to start</span>)</sup>","desc":"Willow, an energetic archaeologist (perhaps suspiciously so) is hunting for her next big discovery. She believes she has found the entrance to ancient underground ruins found to the west of Ice Mountain. There's a catch though - the entrance is sealed tight and she needs to re-unite her old crew to help her break in. Naturally, she has to stay close to the ruins in order to lay claim to the find, so it falls to you to bring her rag-tag group back together for one last caper and a final big pay-off.

Burntof is an old dwarf with a penchant for demolition, Checkal is a well-built lifter of heavy things and Marley is a cunning thief with a knack for disarming traps.

