* The ability to defeat a level 195 &#91;&#91;Jungle Demon&#93;&#93;","desc":"The King of the northern Gnomes, Narnode Shareen, is once again in need of your help. He recently decided to send an envoy of his Royal Guard, the 10th squad, to oversee the decommissioning of the Gnome owned ship-building facilities on the eastern coast of &#91;&#91;Karamja&#93;&#93;.

